  "title": "✈️ (TRAVEL PERKS) JUNIOR BRAND & SALES TRAINEE ✈️",
  "description": "<h2>🤩✈️ Want to develop excellent communication skills AND travel more this 2026? </h2><p><br /><em>🌍 Travel Perks | 🎓 Fresh Grads/ORD Welcome | 🚀 Fast Career Growth </em></p><p><br />Why not do both in your full-time job? Join our team and <strong>level up your communication skills, earn great income,</strong> and <strong>travel across Asia</strong> to learn from top-performing professionals.<br /></p><p><strong>✅ What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li>Represent brands at events & pop-ups</li><li>Engage customers face-to-face</li><li>Work with teams across different countries</li><li>Pick up real-world sales & people skills</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>✈️ Why You’ll Love It</strong></p><ul><li>Regional travel for training & networking</li><li>Young, energetic team culture</li><li>Fast progression into leadership roles</li><li>No experience needed — full training provided</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>👀 You’re Perfect If You…</strong></p><ul><li>Are excited to explore new places</li><li>Want to grow confidence & communication skills</li><li>Love learning by doing</li><li>Are adaptable, driven, and people-oriented</li></ul><p><br />📩 Ready to work, learn, grow — and see the world? <strong>Apply now!</strong></p>",
